{"type": "article", "id": 57545, "title": "易烊千玺代言纪梵希美妆，詹姆斯拍摄耐克新广告片 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-10-22T04:26:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 53626, "name": "Just Do It"}, {"id": 1329, "name": "天猫"}, {"id": 4129, "name": "双 11"}, {"id": 13309, "name": "代言人"}, {"id": 1036, "name": "耐克"}, {"id": 111, "name": "迪士尼"}, {"id": 49264, "name": "易烊千玺"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1375, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181022114540p9WJM3aFyoqLckK2.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/detail/4297106979702910\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>易烊千玺成为纪梵希美妆中国区首位彩妆代言人。</strong></a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181022113309aBSyjZwdkTze0CVI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.388571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>值得一提的 Case</h3><p>迪士尼继续庆祝米奇 90 周年，<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4297665661544578?wm=3333_2001&amp;from=108A093010&amp;sourcetype=weixin\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>与 Skinnydip London 合作了一系列服饰、手机壳与包袋。</strong></a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181022113327B3VkK6NpAfQrhq8e.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181022113328G0iCI3ly1QTELoHR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181022113328wu8LDe5fopGjbZdI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181022113328S8VJhyltAaQfYU1X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4297711022999084?wm=3333_2001&amp;from=108A093010&amp;sourcetype=weixin\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>天猫联合新世相发布一支微电影《裙梦十年》</strong></a>，围绕着裙子、三个女孩十年之间的故事，对应着双 11 十周年的时间点。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=z075804a3pm\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p>​<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/nike-lebron-james-just-ad/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>耐克新推出一支 Just Do It 广告，主角是“小皇帝”詹姆斯。</strong></a>这支广告片追溯了詹姆斯从俄亥俄州的小镇 Akron 进入 NBA 的历程，翻出了不少老照片、旧影像。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=u075961r1n0\"></iframe> </figure> </div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/balenciaga-sued-air-freshener-company-copying-little-trees-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">巴黎世家因涉嫌抄袭被起诉。</a></strong>空气清新剂公司&nbsp;Car-Freshner 正在起诉巴黎世家抄袭，称后者上周推出的新款钥匙扣抄袭了其空气清新剂产品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181022115016vLDeUTYkK7hyrnAj.png\" data-ratio=\"0.934609\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181022115026UBTKflIw7RM8k5pO.png\" data-ratio=\"1.071197\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://adage.com/article/agency-news/good-earnings-day-ipg-q3/315331/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>IPG 公布新季度财报。</strong></a>该季度，IPG 营收增长 3.4% 达到 19 亿美元。排除兼并、收购和汇率影响，有机增幅为 5.4%。IPG 称，这主要受益于其获得的新业务、对 Acxiom Marketing Solutions 收购的完成，同时包装食品客户的业务基调的改善。<br></p><p><br></p><p>题图来自：YouTube@<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=6&amp;v=XMggxvn-6QU\" rel=\"nofollow\">耐克</a><br></p>"}